Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:04.98,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,260)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}好\N夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好热好热  热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中君你从刚才开始就只在说「好热」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就很热了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说「好热」就会更加热了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你说「好热」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好夏  好夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:38.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里田中是故意把夏天好热「なつはあつい」说成热天好夏「あつはなつい」\N在日本是这是著名的大叔冷笑话。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热天好夏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的很夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏过头了啊  好夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好夏好夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想打这家伙一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好夏  真夏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好夏！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.45,-0:00:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shining
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天所有的一切看上去都如此耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气也好  人也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就连这间教室也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天做了作业啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向美绪炫耀一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:03:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧咧咧…咧…咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.63,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(400,600)}日\N常\N之\N48
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明好不容易而且如此难得地做了作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有带啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  让别人给我看看就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的作业是印刷纸啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了祐子  大清早地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业忘记（带）了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷之外星人大侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又忘记（做）了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要轻视我！  我明明有做  只是忘记带了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  我没有轻视你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的作业是国语的印刷纸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是夹在某个地方了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好地找下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才就翻了好几遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}街道会  大福展销会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My  god！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大福展销会是什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  展销会什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到讲台找找的话  也许还有剩余的印刷纸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧不是吧  还有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶可恶  真可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回去拿吗  赶不上的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去拿！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  课要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜咕噜咕噜咕噜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转  转啊转…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快就转它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}急がば回れ原意是欲速则不达，此处借用其表面意思
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.40,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N49
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是像这样每次每次把作业忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天居然是明明做了却又忘在了家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天还真是坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:30.18,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,250)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}名\N片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下我的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:38.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  我该怎样才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:53.35,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,320)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}自\N动\N售\N货\N机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  立花美里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为出新品了啊  我只是在犹豫该买哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这边的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会听你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…饮料很难喝  选旁边的可能会好些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是听从你的推荐才买的呢
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:02.12,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,300)\fad(400,600)}日\N常\N之\N50
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说附近有摊子摆出来了  我决定去看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的就是去玩打靶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我只在电视上看到过  所以今天非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然如此  我只带了500円  没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  一次500万円
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky  刚好500円
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也想吃炒面  但是今天是为这个而来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奖品只有奶糖和茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  只有这些东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只有这些」是指什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里只给品牌商品的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  仅剩的钱都交出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要带奖品回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  一开始就瞄准价格高的可是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是容易打落的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,价格很高吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始要瞄准那些容易打落的才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易打落什么的…剩下的就只有奶糖这个选项了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个奶糖的下面完全粘住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1英寸=1000密尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有几密尔就打落了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  你的素质可真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你是现役的枪手？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这个茄子是纹丝不动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了怎么了  一副泄气的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  你该不会是在想我动了手脚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我的店面看上去有点寒酸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元气满满和不作手脚是绝对可保证的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  这个绝对是耍了什么花招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那个那个  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钉子啊  都能看到钉子了  钉子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是诈骗吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你怎么一句话都不说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你这样的是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是还挺有精神的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来  你也在奶糖下面耍了花招的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为啥要装睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下一发子弹  我到底该瞄准哪个才好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅到掉渣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了哦
