Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我也装了一个
