Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初恋！  在平日的上学路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:17.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飞翔般
